cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep learning based image and sequence inpainting using GANs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of priors and the learning of noise and structural priors, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also deals with video datasets, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the use of recurrent nets, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
